Usage: 
       fastaRename [options] fastaRename 
       parse a file with fasta sequences
       replace the identifier of a fasta sequences by a short identifier
       and generate a file with renamed fasta sequences and a file of mapping


Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -m MAPPING_FILE_NAME, --map=MAPPING_FILE_NAME
                        specify the file to store the mapping
  -o RENAMED_FASTA_NAME, --fasta-out=RENAMED_FASTA_NAME
                        specify the file with the renamed fasta sequences
